<P>
   COLOMBIA-REVOLUTION (San Vicente Del Caguan, Colombia) _ The
dream of a Marxist-Leninist revolution remains improbably alive
amid the rolling cattle pastures and steamy coca fields of southern
Colombia. By Clifford Krauss.
</P>
