<P>
   AUTO-PANOZ (San Antonio) _ Panoz Auto Development was born of
Danny Panoz's desire to build an American sports car. He bought the
manufacturing rights for an Irish company's chassis designed by
engineer Frank Costin, well known for his work with Lotus, Lister
and Maserati. More than a decade after its establishment, Panoz
Auto is producing an ``aluminum intensive vehicle,'' as the creator
calls the Panoz Roadster. By G. CHAMBERS WILLIAMS III.
