Sport Trac is the one that is misnamed. These two vehicles are
identical in concept, yet one is held out to be a version of the
nation's most popular sport-utility vehicle _ the Ford Explorer
while the other is positioned as a version of the nation's most
popular vehicle, period _ the Ford F-150 pickup. By G. CHAMBERS
