to persuade the party's Platform Committee to delete language in
the document that they consider anti-homosexual. But the
conservative Family Values Coalition is fighting the effort.
Meeting today with platform committee chairman Tommy Thompson, the
conservatives say the Log Cabin group is seeking special privileges
for homosexuals. By DAN FREEDMAN.
