<P>
   BULLET-VESTS (Washington) _ Sen. Dianne Feinstein, D-Calif., is
pushing legislation that would punish criminals who use
bullet-proof vests by increasing penalties for those who wear them
while committing a crime. The measure was inspired by the recent
death of a former San Francisco police officer who was shot by a
gunman wearing such a vest. By JUDY HOLLAND.
</P>
