   BRAZIL-FASHION (Sao Paulo) _ On Brazil's growing $18 billion
fashion industry and the effort by its designers to become global
trendsetters. The industry has been energized by the meteoric
success of 19-year-old supermodel Gisele Bundchen. By Jennifer
Rich.
</P>
<P>
   KMART-EARNINGS (Undated) _ Kmart confirmed that it will close 72
stores and take a charge of $740 million before taxes in the second
quarter. Excluding the charge, the company says it expects
operating earnings to fall as much as 75 percent short of analysts'
estimates for the quarter. By Leslie Kaufman.
</P>
<P>
   AT&AMP;T-EARNINGS (Undated)_ AT&AMP;T said its second-quarter earnings
