<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    AIR DELAYS RISE 58 PERCENT IN FIVE YEARS, FEDERAL REPORT SAYS
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (f) financial categories.
 &HT;    By ROB O'DELL
 &HT;    c.2000 Cox News Service
