<P>
   EDITORS: Following is a list of stories related to
AIRFRANCE-CRASH that will move tonight in the New York Times News
Service report. Stories will move in ``i'' news file. For more
information, call toll-free at 888-346-9867. The supervisor is Pat
Ryan.
