u w BC-SUMMIT-REACT-0726-COX     07-25 0957
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-SUMMIT-REACT-0726-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    CAMP DAVID FAILURE LEAVES GREATER UNCERTAINTY IN MIDEAST
 &HT;    With MIDEAST-SUMMIT-0726.
 &HT;    Moving in both (i) International and (w) Washington categories.
 &HT;    By LARRY KAPLOW 
 &HT;    c.2000 Cox News Service 
<TEXT>
