   MIDEAST-ARAB-LEADERS (Cairo) _ Palestinian officials here said
that Yasser Arafat would probably meet soon with many of the Arab
leaders who had urged him to hold firm on his demands for an end to
Israel's 33 years of exclusive control over East Jerusalem and the
Old City. By Susan Sachs.
</P>
