deal-breaker. (Stephen Crowley/The New York Times)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT9) HOLMDEL, N.J. -- July 25, 2000 -- OSBOURNE-OZZFEST --
Heavy metal fans don't usually get the chance to swig a beer and
plunge into a mosh pit. They did  when Ozzy Osbourne's fourth annual
Ozzfest came to the PNC Bank Arts Center here on Monday. The 12-hour
show, with 18 bands all demanding audience participation, was a day
